This paper is primarily focused on image segmentation, which is a core topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also discusses optimization problems and graph theory, which are common in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper mentions interactive segmentation and co-segmentation, which are related to multimedia (cs.MM) and graphics (cs.GR).
